reviewText: I just love New Kids On The Block and this DVD is pretty awesome. Included in this DVD are live performances of "Step By Step", "No More Games", "Tonight", and other great performances by NKOTB. This DVD also includes all of their other hit songs like "Hangin' Tough", "You Got It (The Right Stuff)", and "Cover Girl". NKOTB do an awesome job performing live on stage...the dance moves are wicked awesome. The singing is great. The concert clips are spectacular. I'm still sorry that NKOTB are over now, but that just gives us more room for newer awesome Boy Bands like Backstreet Boys, 98 Degrees, and O-Town. If you are a true fan of New Kids On The Block, then you must own this DVD. Oh yeah...and today I just saw the E! True Hollywood Story on New Kids On The Block and that was pretty cool, too. I'm glad they are all on their own with solo careers, and wish them all the best of luck.
summary: Fantastic DVD from a fantastic group!
